name: Pedal Power 4x4
details:
4x4 Isolated Power SupplyThe Voodoo Lab Pedal Power 4x4 is an isolated power supply designed to make your high-current DSP-based effects pedals sound their best. With eight totally isolated, regulated, and filtered output sections, Pedal Power 4x4 keeps your pedals quiet and free of the high-frequency hash that happens when you use digital switching power supplies. Power up to eight of your power-hungry digital effects; this roadworthy pro unit will give you clean, consistent power - even under funky AC line conditions often encountered onstage. Enjoy lower noise and improved tone with the Voodoo Lab Pedal Power 4x4.
